        <p>Pehle ek baat clear kar dein — grey hair hona ek natural process hai. Umar ke saath har insaan ke hair grey happen. Lekin jab ye time from pehle hone lage — 20s ya early 30s mein — toh ye premature greying hai and iska matlab hai of kuch toh galat ho raha hai body mein. Aur agar sahi time pe dhyan diya jaaye toh bahut cases mein grey hair ko slow, stop, and kuch hadh tak reverfrom also ofya ja sakta hai.</p>

