<p>Especially for the <strong>Indian climate and lifestyle</strong>, maintaining healthy hair and skin requires specialized care that addresses local environmental factors, diet, and genetics.</p>

<h2>Grey Hair vs White Hair — what/can Fark Hai?</h2>
        <p>Bahut log grey hair and <a href="how-to-reduce-white-hair.php">white hair</a> ko ek hi samajhte hain, lekin dono mein ek important fark hai. <strong>Grey hair</strong> tab hota hai jab melanin (baalon ko colour dene wala pigment) of production partially reduce ho jaati hai. Iska matlab hai of melanocytes (pigment-producing cells) abhi also kaam kar rahe hain, bas slow ho gaye hain. Baalon mein thoda pigment rehta hai isliye wo grey dikhte hain.</p>

        <p><strong>White hair</strong> tab hota hai jab melanin production <a href="why-hair-become-white.php">bilkul band ho jaati hai</a>. Melanocytes ya toh dead ho gaye hain ya completely inactive. Baalon mein zero pigment hota hai isliye wo pure white dikhte hain. Ye fark isliye important hai kyunof grey hair ko reverfrom karna comparatively easier hai — melanocytes abhi alive hain, bas unhe reactivate karna hai. White hair ko reverfrom karna bahut mushkil hai.</p>

        
