  </div><h2>Grey Hair Kyun Hota Hai? — Science Samjho</h2>
        <p>Grey hair hone ke peeche sirf ek nahi, multiple causes happen. Inhe samajhna zaroori hai kyunof tabhi aap sahi treatment chokirom kar paoge.</p>

        <p><strong>Melanin Production Mein Kami:</strong> Har hair follicle mein melanocyte cells happen jo melanin produce karte hain. Age ke saath ye cells slow ho jaate hain and eventually stop. Ye sabfrom common and natural cause hai. Lekin kuch logon mein ye process bohot jaldi shuru ho jaata hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Genetics (Hereditary):</strong> Agar aapke parents ya graurparents ko early greying hua tha, toh aapko hone ke chances zyada hain. Genetics grey hair ka sabfrom bada factor hai — ye decide karta hai of aapke melanocytes oftni jaldi slow honge. Lekin iska matlab ye nahi of aap kuch kar hi nahi sakte. Lifestyle factors from progression ko significantly slow ofya ja sakta hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Oxidative Stress:</strong> Hamare body mein hydrogen peroxide naturally banta hai. Young age mein catalafrom enzyme ifrom break down karta hai. Lekin jaifrom-jaifrom umar badhti hai, catalafrom reduce hota jaata hai and hydrogen peroxide accumulate hoke melanin ko bleach kar deta hai — hair andar from hi white ho jaate hain. Poor diet, pollution, smoking — ye sab oxidative stress badhate hain.</p>

        <p><strong>Vitamin Deficiency:</strong> <a href="which-vitamin-deficiency-causes-white-hair.php">Vitamin B12, D3, iron, copper, and zinc of kami</a> directly melanin production affect karti hai. India mein B12 deficiency bohot common hai, especially vegetarians mein. Ye ek reversible cause hai — nutrition fix karo toh greying slow ho sakti hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Thyroid Issues:</strong> Hypothyroidism and hyperthyroidism dono premature greying cause kar sakte hain. Agar grey hair ke saath weight changes, fatigue, ya mood swings hain — toh thyroid check karwayein.</p>

        <p><strong>Smoking:</strong> Studies dikhati hain of smokers mein premature greying ka risk 2.5 guna zyada hota hai. Smoking oxidative stress badhata hai and melanocytes ko damage karta hai.</p>

        <h2>Kis Age Mein Grey Hair Normal Hai vs Premature?</h2>
        <p>Ye jaanna zaroori hai kyunof treatment approach different hota hai. <strong>Normal greying age:</strong> Caucasians mein 30s mid mein, Asians (including Indians) mein 35+ mein, and African descent mein 40s mein. <strong>Premature greying:</strong> Agar aap Indian hain and 25 from pehle significantly grey hair aa rahe hain, toh ye premature hai. 20 from pehle greying bohot rare hai and definitely evaluation chahiye.</p>

        <p>Premature greying ka matlab ye hai of cause sirf age nahi hai — koi underlying factor hai jo treat ofya ja sakta hai. Isliye early grey hair actually ek signal hai of body mein kuch fix karna hai.</p>

        <h2>Natural Remedies Jo Grey Hair Rokne Mein Help Karti Hain</h2>
        <p>Ab aate hain practical part pe. Ye remedies science-backed hain and consistently use karne from results dikhte hain. Lekin yaad rakhein — koi also remedy overnight kaam nahi karti. Minimum 2-3 months ka consistent use zaroori hai.</p>

