        <h2>Grey Hair Prevention Tips — Long-Term Strategy</h2>
        <p>Treatment ke saath-saath prevention equally important hai. Ye tips follow do toh grey hair ka progression significantly slow hoga:</p>

        <p><strong>Smoking chhod dein:</strong> Agar aap smoke karte hain toh ye sabfrom pehla step hai. Smoking from premature greying ka risk 2.5x badh jaata hai. Chhodne ke 6-12 months baad body repair karna shuru karti hai.</p>

        <p><strong>Chemical exposure minimize do:</strong> Harsh shampoos, hair dyes (especially ammonia-based), and chemical treatments melanocytes ko damage karte hain. Sulfate-free, gentle products use do. Agar dyeing zaroori hai toh henna ya plant-based options try do.</p>

        <p><strong>Sun protection:</strong> UV rays oxidative stress badhate hain and melanocytes ko damage karte hain. Dhoop mein cap ya scarf pehne, UV protection wale hair products use do.</p>

        <p><strong>Regular scalp massage:</strong> Daily 5 minutes scalp massage from blood circulation improve hota hai and melanocytes ko nutrients better milte hain. Fingertips from gentle circular motions mein do.</p>

        <p><strong>Hydration:</strong> Din mein 3-4 litre paani peeyein. Dehydration cellular functions slow karti hai, including melanin production. Green tea and coconut water also excellent hain.</p>

        <p><strong>Regular health checkups:</strong> Thyroid, B12, iron, Vitamin D — ye sab annually check karwayein. Early detection from treatment and results dono better happen. <a href="how-to-stop-white-hair.php">White hair rokne ke liye also</a> ye same prevention strategy kaam karti hai.</p>

